Summary:
Nadia demonstrated solid foundational experience across Kubernetes, containers, SRE, and development, meeting the minimum bar for the role. She showed a strong learning attitude and adaptability, particularly when exposed to areas she has not previously worked in. Based on her overall experience and depth, she appears to be operating at an early VP (Value Professional / mid-level) rather than a senior or staff level. Nevertheless, her mindset and communication strengths make her a viable candidate for further evaluation.
Strengths:
