Weaknesses / Areas to Validate in Next Round:
Container expertise is somewhat limited; while she understands container builds and basic best practices, she lacks depth in advanced topics such as multi-stage builds.
Development experience is limited; although she has worked with Python and Go, she did not demonstrate experience building or owning complex applications end-to-end.
Engineering depth should be further validated, particularly around application design and implementation.
Conclusion:
We recommend progressing Nadia to the next interview round. The final interview should focus on validating her development depth and container expertise, while assessing whether her current experience level aligns with the expectations of the role. Her communication skills, growth mindset, and strong Kubernetes/SRE background are clear positives for the team.
